description:
“Furious Finn Survival Tip #109: Always bring your own toilet paper.”

Tough. Resourceful. Prepared. Finn travels the world in his V8 super car defeating bad guys and outrunning the law. He lives by his own code and is constantly looking over his shoulder. He has no friends and trusts nobody. But millions of people read his blog - they're even turning it into a book! People can't get enough of his survival tips and tales of escaping from tight situations.
(Exclusive on Xbox One)
name: Furious Finn

description:
“Which records does Krezak hold, you ask? What a ridiculous question. He holds them all.”

The son of a wealthy nobleman, Krezak spent his days dodging responsibilities and chasing trouble. That is, until he was asked by some locals to join a soccer game. The rest is history. Now known as the greatest athlete of his generation – if not all time – the people’s adoration for him is almost as great as his love to compete.
 
Off the field he has earned a reputation for being a bit of a joker, but it has always been harmless fun. Except that one time involving the crane and peanut butter...
(Exclusive on Xbox One)
name: Krezak: The Legend

description:
“All he needs is a million to one shot.”

Raised in the urban sprawl, Berrik dreams of making it big and providing a better life for his family.  He has fast hands, smooth moves, and a mouth that never stops talking. Following a gruelling regimen of jogging, racing games, and pickup basketball, Berrik is determined to become the first boxing champion from his block. Now all he needs is a gruff but stern coach, and oh yeah, a membership at the boxing gym down the street.
(Exclusive on Xbox One)
name: Berrik: The Boxer

description:
“The oceans are controlled by the pirates, and the pirates are controlled by Ez.”

After graduating at the top of her class, Ezebel could have been anything she wanted – so, logically, she chose to be a pirate. Why? Well because being a pirate is pretty awesome. Even more awesome is establishing yourself as Queen of all Pirates in just over a year (a pirate record by the way). Just as she shined at her studies, so she has excelled as a leader of swashbuckling buccaneers. You want anything done on the ocean, well you will have to talk to Ez first.
(Exclusive on Xbox One)
name: Ezebel: The Pirate Queen

description:
"What looks like the end, is often just the beginning."

To call Amelia determined would be an understatement. She leaves no mystery unsolved, no border uncrossed, and no challenge unaccepted! When everyone else has given up, she's just getting started. When it looks like she's down and out, Amelia comes back stronger than ever. If she can't find a way, well, Amelia makes one. Dark tunnels, creepy crawlies, and haunted houses are no match for her curiosity, wit, and tenacity!
(Exclusive on Xbox One)
